<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感恩節<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />能不能快點開始啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那位一流主廚已經在廣場待命了，<delay20 />
