<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你問我？<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的話……<delay20 />
